        {
            "id": "https://jakwoda.github.io/riso/",
            "url": "https://jakwoda.github.io/riso/",
            "title": "Riso 🖨️",
            "summary": "Challange Translating digital artwork into Risograph prints involves significant technical \"guesswork\" due to unpredictable ink overlaps, which creates barriers for&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<h1> </h1>\n<h2 class=\"dropcap\">Challange</h2>\n<p>Translating digital artwork into Risograph prints involves significant technical \"guesswork\" due to unpredictable ink overlaps, which creates barriers for non-experts and leads to confussion during workshops as well as time and material waste. It was prepared for Obra Press to help them run workshops without too much laptops. </p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/gallery/untitled12345-5-1.png\" data-size=\"468x712\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/gallery/untitled12345-5-1-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"a mockup of an app on a mobile device\" width=\"468\" height=\"712\"></a>\n<figcaption>a mockup of an app on a mobile device</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<h2 class=\"dropcap\">Approach</h2>\n<p> Developed an interactive web-based simulation using p5.js that mimics the behavior of Riso inks. The system was built as an open and educational tool to help artists understand the relationship between digital design and analog print processes through real-time color modeling. </p>\n<figure class=\"post__image\"><img loading=\"lazy\"  src=\"https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/Screenshot-2023-02-27-at-20.37.00.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2686\" height=\"1688\" sizes=\"(max-width: 48em) 100vw, 100vw\" srcset=\"https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/responsive/Screenshot-2023-02-27-at-20.37.00-xs.webp 300w ,https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/responsive/Screenshot-2023-02-27-at-20.37.00-sm.webp 480w ,https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/responsive/Screenshot-2023-02-27-at-20.37.00-md.webp 768w\"></figure>\n<p> </p>\n<h2 class=\"dropcap\">Outcome</h2>\n<p>The prototype became a practical visualisation aid that bridged digital and analog workflows, making print design more accessible, sustainable, and transparent for independent artists and newbies. It was a start of my journey into accessible design.<br>Published in Slanted Magazine “Digital Tools” </p>\n<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\"  data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/gallery/untitled12345-6.png\" data-size=\"1043x611\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/gallery/untitled12345-6-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"a picture of a print on a webshop \" width=\"768\" height=\"450\"></a>\n<figcaption>a picture of a print on a webshop</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/gallery/untitled12345-1.png\" data-size=\"360x516\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/gallery/untitled12345-1-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"a test o duotone risoprint\" width=\"360\" height=\"516\"></a>\n<figcaption>a test o duotone risoprint</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/gallery/untitledggg_-1.png\" data-size=\"502x502\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://jakwoda.github.io/media/posts/1/gallery/untitledggg_-1-thumbnail.webp\" alt=\"test of mono color risoprint with strong dithering\" width=\"502\" height=\"502\"></a>\n<figcaption>test of mono color risoprint with strong dithering</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</div></div>\n<p> </p>",
